  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n                        \u003cp\u003eIn the heart of Desio, Italy, a modest 700-square-foot apartment has been transformed into a space of connection and emotion. This renovation project, named \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/DCahlNlI4fV/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOde to the Moon\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, was led by \u003ca href=\"https://www.behance.net/paradisiartificiali\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStudio Paradisiartificiali\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e with the creative guidance of stylist \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/giulia_taglialatela/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eGiulia Taglialatela\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, as a tribute to the profound bond between a mother and daughter. A home designed to reunite, nurture, and reflect the intangible ties that link two generations of women.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=564312\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-564312\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-2-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Room with green leaf-patterned wallpaper, terracotta flooring, large planters, and wooden shelves separating dining and living areas. Bright window view and various plants enhance the space.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-2-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-2-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/O