Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-8-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-8.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=564319\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-564319\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-9-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A kitchen with green cabinets, a wooden countertop, a white sink, and a tiled backsplash. A shelf with decorative items is next to a wallpapered wall with a leafy pattern, leading to a cozy room.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-9-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-9-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-9-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-9.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=564320\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-564320\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-10-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A kitchen with green cabinets, a wooden countertop, built-in oven, and leafy wallpaper. A striped rug and various kitchen items are visible on the countertop.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-10-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-10-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-10-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-10.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhere greenery and clay do not dominate, an ethereal whiteness takes over – a representation of clouds that fill the space with lightness and serenity. The apartment, though physically compact, becomes expansive, inviting its residents to explore not just its corners but their own depths.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=564321\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-564321\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-11-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A kitchen with light green cabinets, a white sink, and a wooden countertop. Fresh produce is on the counter, including grapes, pineapple, and kale. A white towel hangs by the sink.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-11-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-11-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-11-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-11-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-11.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=564322\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-564322\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-12-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Two ceramic jars labeled \u0026#34;Riso\u0026#34; and \u0026#34;Caffe\u0026#34; on a wooden countertop next to an orange pitcher with leafy greens, against a white tiled wall.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-12-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-12-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-12-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-12-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-12.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAs dusk descends, the journey leads to a hidden sanctuary within the garden – the nymphaeum, a place of water and stillness. Here, time seems to pause, offering a moment of introspection and rebirth. In this quiet area, the spirit of the home reveals itself fully: a space not just for living but for transformation and self-discovery.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=564323\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-564323\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-13-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A bedroom with an open window, light-colored walls, a green bed with patterned pillows and blankets, a potted plant on the sill, and a chair and racks with clothes near the bed.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-13-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-13-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-13-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-13-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-13.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=564324\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-564324\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-14-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A cozy bedroom with a white chair holding books and decor, next to a mint green bed with blue-gray bedding. A leafy wall art piece hangs above, and a potted plant is nearby.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-14-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-14-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-14-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-14-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-14.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=564325\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-564325\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-15-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A bathroom with blue tiled walls, lush green plants around the bathtub, a butterfly, and decorative wall art.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-15-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-15-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-15-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-15-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-15.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAt the heart of this project lies an ode to the Moon – a symbol of intuition, mystery, and the feminine essence. The Moon, with its ever-shifting phases, mirrors the fluidity of human emotions and the complexity of the mother-daughter relationship. The poetic invocation to the Moon, recited in the imagined sanctuary, captures the essence of this connection:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eOh, Moon,\u003cbr/\u003e\nI have crossed valleys and rivers to reach you.\u003cbr/\u003e\nI have slept on the bare ground and under the watchful gaze of an owl.\u003cbr/\u003e\nThe more I sought the Way to find you, the more lost I became.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eIt was you who asked me to lose myself so that I would discover that there is no one way;\u003c/em\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cem\u003ethere are many.\u003c/em\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cem\u003eThe creatures of the night guard your secret.\u003c/em\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cem\u003eQueen of intuition, Queen of dreams. You defy reason.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eI abandon myself to the oblivion of your hypnotic gaze.\u003c/em\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cem\u003eThe more I flee from the unknown, the more I desire you.\u003c/em\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cem\u003eNot a warm embrace but an evanescent caress you have for me.\u003c/em\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cem\u003eNot a clear image, but an arcane vision.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eA silver mirror reveals your face, but it was only an enchantment.\u003c/em\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cem\u003eI drive into your opaline veil, the illusion of drinking from your fountain.\u003c/em\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cem\u003eThen you silently vanish, and everything around me falls silent.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eIn an endless cycle I keep searching for you\u003c/em\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cem\u003eIn an endless cycle I find my shadow.\u003c/em\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cem\u003eLike a handmaiden faithful to her Queen\u003c/em\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cem\u003eI come back to you, wrapped in the mystery of your icy Light.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe Moon becomes a metaphor for the elusive yet magnetic pull of the unknown – a reminder that life’s most profound journeys are often those that lead us into uncharted territory.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=564326\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-564326\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-16-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bathroom with a curved wooden vanity, blue tiles, and a round mirror. Wall inscription reads, \u0026#34;I am the moon, your eternal mirror.\u0026#34; Decor includes artwork and a small mirror.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-16-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-16-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-16-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-16-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-16.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=564327\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-564327\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-17-810x608.jpg\" alt=\"Bathroom with blue tiles, an oval mirror, a circular light, artwork, and text on the wall. A wooden vanity with white countertop holds toiletries and flowers.\" width=\"810\" height=\"608\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-17-810x608.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-17-800x600.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-17-768x576.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-17.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=564328\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-564328\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-18-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Bathroom with wood vanity, oval mirror, blue tiles, and a white countertop. A small bowl with pink flowers is on the counter next to soap and a seashell.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-18-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-18-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-18-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-18-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-18.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=564329\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-564329\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-19-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A stone relief sculpture depicting human figures is mounted on a white wall. Above it is a round wall ornament with a face, and below is a blue-tiled surface.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-19-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-19-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-19-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-19-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/Ode-to-the-Moon-Apartment-Italy-Paradisiartificiali-19.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTo see more projects by by Studio Paradisiartificiali, click \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/paradisiartificiali.it/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003ehere\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003ePhotography by \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/valentinasommariva/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eValentina Sommariva\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n                        \n                                                    \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson-100x100.jpg\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson.jpg 2x\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" alt=\"\"/\u003e                                    \u003c/p\u003e\n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003eCaroline Williamson is Editor-in-Chief of Design Milk. She has a BFA in photography from SCAD and can usually be found searching for vintage wares, doing New York Times crossword puzzles in pen, or reworking playlists on Spotify.\u003c/p\u003e\n                                    \n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n                            \u003c/div\u003e\n                                            \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
